<br />B = 5
<br />C = 3
<br />X = (A*0.6) + (B*0.2) + (C*0.3)
<br />Then I need the int from X to do some other calculations.
<br />
<br />2. Is there any way to get a random number from 0~9?
<br />It's so easy to do with javascript, but with 6502...no idea. <img src="./images/smilies/icon_redface.gif" alt=":oops:" title="Embarassed" /></div>

